# moomoo OpenD credentials for the tms-live node (mounted as an env_file).
#
# For P5 MARKET-DATA + signal mode against a LOCAL OpenD (127.0.0.1:11111 on the
# host, encrypt=off) NO credentials are required — this file may be left absent.
# These knobs exist for the deferred real-OpenD smoke / future paper/live (P6),
# where OpenD is logged in on the host with a real Futu/moomoo account.
#
# Copy to secrets/moomoo.env and fill in as needed. NEVER commit secrets/moomoo.env
# (it is gitignored). The values are read from the process environment and are
# NEVER logged by tms-live.

# Optional RSA private-key path for OpenD encrypted transport (only if OpenD is
# configured with encryption; localhost market-data uses encrypt=off).
# TMS_MOOMOO_RSA_KEY_PATH=/run/secrets/opend_rsa.pem

# Optional OpenD unlock-trade password hash (P6 paper/live only; unused in P5).
# TMS_MOOMOO_UNLOCK_PWD_MD5=
